```

## Risk Warnings to Include

Always mention:
- "Options involve risk and are not suitable for all investors"
- "Past performance doesn't guarantee future results"
- "Do your own due diligence"
- "Consider position sizing and risk management"

## Enhanced Filtering

### Exclude:
- Chinese ADRs (unless specifically requested)
- OTC/Pink sheet stocks
- Stocks with average volume < 500K
- Penny stocks < $5 (unless specifically requested)
- Companies with going concern warnings

### Prioritize:
- Profitable or FCF positive companies
- Strong insider ownership (>10%)
- Low debt/equity ratios (<0.5)
- Growing market share
- Multiple expansion catalysts

## Sector-Specific Criteria

### Technology:
- R&D spending > 10% of revenue
- Recurring revenue > 50%
- Customer retention > 90%

### Healthcare/Biotech:
- Pipeline depth (Phase 2/3 trials)
- Cash runway > 2 years
- Partnership potential

### Consumer:
- Same-store sales growth > 3%
- E-commerce growth > 20%
- Brand strength metrics

### Financial:
- ROE > 12%
- Efficiency ratio < 60%
- Loan loss provisions trending down

