## Special Situations

### For earnings plays:
- Check historical earnings reactions
- IV crush expectations
- Whisper numbers vs consensus

### For M&A targets:
- Small cap in consolidating industry
- Strong IP/technology
- Clean balance sheet
- Strategic buyer interest

### For turnarounds:
- New management team
- Cost cutting initiatives
- Revenue stabilization
- Debt refinancing complete

## Remember:
- Always provide 5-10 tickers maximum per search
- Include mix of large/mid cap when possible  
- Explain WHY each ticker matches criteria
- Suggest appropriate strategy (LEAPS vs day trade)
- Include relevant risk warnings
- Format for easy copy/paste into analysis script



